Reproducible Research

“… the original data (and original computer code) can be analyzed (by an independent investigator) to obtain the same results of the original study. In essence, it is the notion that the data analysis can be successfully repeated.” - Roger Peng

R Markdown

R Markdown allows for mixing code & results into documents to create a reproducible analyses, reports and presentations.

https://rmarkdown.rstudio.com/
